data.description: You won't want to miss this one, perfect location. 3 Bedroom, 2 Bath, Paver Drive, Impact Windows and Doors, Pocketing Slider to the Screened Lanai, New Seawall on Fresh Water Canal, No Flood Zone, Granite Counter Tops, Wood Cabinets, Large Master Bedroom/Bath offers, Dual Sinks & Granite Counters, Oversized Closet and much more.  This home has upgraded Lighting, 6 panel interior doors, Ceiling Fans and Stainless Steel Appliances. Great Southern rear exposure to add your pool if desired. Close to Shopping and Dining in the fast growing Pine Island Rd & Del Prado Blvd intersection. Surrounded by newer homes in a desirable neighborhood. City Utilities are in, some assessments remain.
